CLOUD MODELS :
ON PEM 
IAAS
PAS
SAS

    CLOUD SERVICE MODELS – SHORT NOTES

    --------------------------------------------------
    1) ON-PREMISES (ON-PREM)
    --------------------------------------------------

        • Everything is managed by you.
        • Physical servers in your office/data center.
        • You manage:
              - Hardware
              - Networking
              - Storage
              - OS
              - Applications
              - Security

        High control
        High responsibility
        High maintenance cost


    --------------------------------------------------
    2) IaaS (Infrastructure as a Service)
    --------------------------------------------------

        • Cloud provider manages:
              - Hardware
              - Networking
              - Data center

        • You manage:
              - Operating System
              - Applications
              - Runtime
              - Data

        Example services:
              - EC2
              - Virtual Machines
              - EBS
			  - EFS 

        Most flexible model.


    --------------------------------------------------
    3) PaaS (Platform as a Service)
    --------------------------------------------------

        • Cloud provider manages:
              - Hardware
              - OS
              - Runtime
              - Middleware

        • You manage:
              - Application code
              - Data

        Example:
              - AWS Elastic Beanstalk
              - Azure App Service

        Good for developers.


    --------------------------------------------------
    4) SaaS (Software as a Service)
    --------------------------------------------------

        • Cloud provider manages everything.
        • You only use the software.

        Example:
              - Gmail
              - Microsoft 365
              - Salesforce

        No infrastructure management.


    --------------------------------------------------
    SIMPLE COMPARISON
    --------------------------------------------------

        On-Prem → You manage everything  
        IaaS    → You manage OS + apps  
        PaaS    → You manage only app code  
        SaaS    → You just use the software  


